lowing reaction is in GRI30, but not in the H2/O2 subset:

H+O2+M<=3D>HO2+M=
                           2.800E+18    -.860        .00
O2/ .00/ H2O/ .00/=
 AR/ .00/ 

When I include it with the h2o2.inp reactions, I get the same r=

as the gri30.inp reactions give.

tion was excluded? Seems kinda
important to me.
